description:
&lt;p&gt;South Reading and Shinfield Group Medical Practice is a well-established NHS GP surgery in Reading, split across two sites, with approximately 10, 000 registered patients. We are a friendly, supportive, practice that has as a committed multi-professional team. We currently use the Emis Web clinical system.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time position (37.5 hours) and will be during our opening hours 07:45-18:30 Monday to Friday. We also offer extended hours on a Saturday 08:00-13:00.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have and be able to demonstrate:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Good customer service skills. Previous NHS GP Practice experience is desirable but not essential;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Friendly and approachable manner;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Experience of working in a team;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Good telephone manner;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Adept in using own initiative when working alone;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Experience working in a busy environment;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· The ability to multitask and prioritise effectively whilst staying calm under pressure;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Has a good understanding of confidentiality;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Flexibility in working pattern and duties;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Ability to cope with and manage change;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Computer literate. EmisWeb familiarity is desirable but training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For immediate start.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must have the right to work in the EU as we are unable to provide sponsorship or assistance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Employment subject to a standard DBS check&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Application Deadline: 11/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview date:16/11/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Types: Full-time, Permanent. Exact shifts to be agreed with suitable candidates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary: £9.00 per hour&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company pension&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sick pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;healthcare (preferably NHS GP): 1 year (Required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work remotely:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
